graph TD
    TaskExec[Task Execution in Container] --> FailDetect{Failure Detected by AM?}
    FailDetect -->|No| Success[Task Completed]
    FailDetect -->|Yes| AnalyzeFailure{Type of Failure?}
    
    AnalyzeFailure -->|Container Crashed / Network| RetryTask[Re-run Task in New Container]
    AnalyzeFailure -->|Data Read / Fetch Error| IdentifySource[Locate Upstream Task Source]
    IdentifySource --> RescheduleUpstream[Re-run Upstream Task to Regenerate Intermediate Data]
    
    RetryTask --> LimitCheck{Retry Limit Reached?}
    RescheduleUpstream --> LimitCheck
    
    LimitCheck -->|No| TaskExec
    LimitCheck -->|Yes| FailVertex[Fail Active Vertex]
    
    FailVertex --> VertexLimit{Vertex Retry Limit Reached?}
    VertexLimit -->|No| RerunVertex[Re-execute Vertex Tasks]
    VertexLimit -->|Yes| FailDAG[Abort DAG Job & Notify Client]
    
    RerunVertex --> TaskExec
